      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Material properties sourced from coupon testing of the same Ti-6Al-4V lot; geometric dimensions from CMM measurements of test specimens.",
      "rationale": "Material properties (elastic modulus, yield strength, tangent modulus) were derived from uniaxial tensile coupon tests on the same material lot as the test constructs. Geometry was characterized by coordinate measuring machine (CMM) measurements of representative specimens, ensuring high fidelity between model inputs and physical test articles."
    },
    {
