      "rationale": "The validation activities directly replicate the COU: the same non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw geometry, ASTM F1717 compression-bending loading configuration, and two-laboratory testing protocol. ASTM F1717 is the FDA-recognized consensus standard for spinal implant mechanical testing, confirming high relevance of the validation activities to the regulatory COU."
